### Verificar servidor
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Listar eventos
GET http://localhost:3000/events

### Calcular resumen de checkout
POST http://localhost:3000/checkout/summary
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Registrar pedido
POST http://localhost:3000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}
